00:57:25.963 --> 00:57:28.465 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to conclude our convention.

00:57:28.465 --> 00:57:30.217 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Enjoy this video.

00:57:52.197 --> 00:57:57.328 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Why should I fear the lion?

00:57:59.330 --> 00:58:04.918 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Why should I fear any foe?

00:58:04.918 --> 00:58:08.839 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With Jehovah by my side,

00:58:08.839 --> 00:58:12.259 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I will not run and hide.

00:58:12.259 --> 00:58:18.182 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My God is with me; this I know.

00:58:18.182 --> 00:58:20.809 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

00:58:20.809 --> 00:58:25.189 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I see beyond the darkness.

00:58:25.189 --> 00:58:27.775 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

00:58:27.775 --> 00:58:31.612 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
there’s nothing more to fear.

00:58:32.321 --> 00:58:36.200 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With Jehovah, I am strong,

00:58:36.200 --> 00:58:40.079 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Determined to go on,

00:58:40.079 --> 00:58:45.542 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Knowing that my God is always near—

00:58:45.542 --> 00:58:50.214 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith.

00:59:00.974 --> 00:59:07.356 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Those faithful ones before us

00:59:07.356 --> 00:59:13.529 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Lived their lives in loyalty.

00:59:13.529 --> 00:59:17.324 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
By their faith they endured.

00:59:17.324 --> 00:59:20.744 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Their future is assured.

00:59:20.744 --> 00:59:25.791 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They’ll stand again for all to see.

00:59:26.750 --> 00:59:29.420 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

00:59:29.420 --> 00:59:33.549 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I see beyond the darkness.

00:59:33.549 --> 00:59:36.009 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

00:59:36.009 --> 00:59:40.639 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
there’s nothing more to fear.

00:59:40.639 --> 00:59:44.309 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With Jehovah, I am strong,

00:59:44.309 --> 00:59:48.439 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Determined to go on,

00:59:48.439 --> 00:59:54.153 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Knowing that my God is always near—

00:59:54.153 --> 00:59:58.365 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith.

00:59:58.365 --> 01:00:05.289 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith, I can move a mountain.

01:00:05.289 --> 01:00:12.421 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith, my hope is sure.

01:00:12.421 --> 01:00:14.673 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Where would I be

01:00:14.673 --> 01:00:19.011 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Without the faith that helps me see

01:00:19.011 --> 01:00:27.603 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Beyond the trials I endure?

01:00:29.771 --> 01:00:36.570 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I see the wondrous future

01:00:36.570 --> 01:00:41.492 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God has in store for me.

01:00:43.118 --> 01:00:46.288 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I need to be strong.

01:00:46.288 --> 01:00:49.458 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I know it won’t be long

01:00:49.458 --> 01:00:55.881 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Till Jehovah claims his victory.

01:00:55.881 --> 01:00:58.467 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

01:00:58.467 --> 01:01:02.804 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I see beyond the darkness.

01:01:02.804 --> 01:01:05.224 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

01:01:05.224 --> 01:01:09.853 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
there’s nothing more to fear.

01:01:09.853 --> 01:01:13.774 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With Jehovah, I am strong,

01:01:13.774 --> 01:01:17.528 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Determined to go on,

01:01:17.528 --> 01:01:23.534 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Knowing that my God is always near—

01:01:26.870 --> 01:01:31.625 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

01:01:40.759 --> 01:01:48.684 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith.

01:01:51.562 --> 01:01:55.440 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What a powerfully motivating video!

01:01:55.440 --> 01:01:59.194 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And we look forward to singing that song

01:01:59.194 --> 01:02:02.656 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to conclude our convention.

01:02:02.656 --> 01:02:04.992 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Dear brothers and sisters,

01:02:04.992 --> 01:02:06.994 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
faithful children,

01:02:06.994 --> 01:02:09.538 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
cherished interested ones,

01:02:09.538 --> 01:02:12.666 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
there’s no doubt that right now

01:02:12.666 --> 01:02:16.169 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we face powerful enemies.

01:02:16.169 --> 01:02:19.590 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For one thing, we have a powerful enemy

01:02:19.590 --> 01:02:21.633 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
inside our bodies

01:02:21.633 --> 01:02:23.635 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—inherited sin.

01:02:23.635 --> 01:02:28.724 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It wages an intense war
against our desire to do what is right.

01:02:29.683 --> 01:02:33.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Secondly, we have the formidable foes:

01:02:33.687 --> 01:02:36.773 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Satan and his demons.

01:02:36.773 --> 01:02:40.360 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Satan is described as a devouring lion,

01:02:40.360 --> 01:02:42.362 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a cunning serpent,

01:02:42.362 --> 01:02:44.448 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a fierce dragon,

01:02:44.448 --> 01:02:46.450 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a sneaky birdcatcher,

01:02:46.450 --> 01:02:49.161 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and he’s given other evil descriptions.

01:02:49.161 --> 01:02:51.580 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ephesians 6:12 says:

01:02:51.580 --> 01:02:56.084 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We have a struggle
[the footnote, literally “a wrestling”]

01:02:56.084 --> 01:03:01.089 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
. . . against the wicked spirit forces
in the heavenly places.”

01:03:01.089 --> 01:03:05.385 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And as mentioned in our publications,
there may be tens of thousands

01:03:05.385 --> 01:03:08.805 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of these powerful, evil spirit creatures

01:03:08.805 --> 01:03:10.807 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the invisible realm

01:03:10.807 --> 01:03:15.145 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
waging war against us.

01:03:15.145 --> 01:03:19.650 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thirdly, we have this wicked world
all around us

01:03:19.650 --> 01:03:22.402 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that is trying to assimilate us

01:03:22.402 --> 01:03:26.782 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
into joining them in ungodly conduct.

01:03:26.782 --> 01:03:28.950 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And looking at the ratio,

01:03:28.950 --> 01:03:33.205 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we as Jehovah’s people
are outnumbered by people of the world

01:03:33.205 --> 01:03:37.751 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by about 900 to 1.

01:03:37.751 --> 01:03:42.547 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But despite the power
of those three great enemies,

01:03:42.547 --> 01:03:47.552 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
our faith—this product
of Jehovah’s invincible holy spirit—

01:03:48.303 --> 01:03:53.266 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
makes us stronger and stronger individually

01:03:53.266 --> 01:03:57.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
than all of those three enemies combined.

01:03:58.605 --> 01:04:00.649 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the near future,

01:04:00.649 --> 01:04:03.985 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
another powerful enemy will come against us.

01:04:03.985 --> 01:04:06.863 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This formidable foe

01:04:06.863 --> 01:04:11.868 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is a coalition of nations
called Gog in Ezekiel chapter 38.

01:04:11.868 --> 01:04:16.873 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And Ezekiel chapter 38 says
that Gog will come with “a great assembly,

01:04:16.873 --> 01:04:18.959 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a vast army.”

01:04:18.959 --> 01:04:21.545 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Like clouds covering the land,”

01:04:21.545 --> 01:04:25.215 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
they will come against God’s people.

01:04:25.215 --> 01:04:28.802 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, this could be
a very intimidating situation.

01:04:28.802 --> 01:04:30.804 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But dear brothers and sisters,

01:04:30.804 --> 01:04:35.809 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
your faith will make you stronger than Gog

01:04:35.809 --> 01:04:38.103 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and will keep you strong

01:04:38.103 --> 01:04:42.023 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
until Jehovah miraculously intervenes
at Armageddon.

01:04:42.023 --> 01:04:45.652 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And if you think about it,
Armageddon really is a rescue operation.

01:04:45.652 --> 01:04:47.654 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He will intervene,

01:04:47.654 --> 01:04:52.492 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and he will sweep attacking Gog away forever

01:04:52.492 --> 01:04:56.538 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with a “broom of annihilation.”

01:04:56.538 --> 01:05:00.876 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the past, faith has helped God’s people

01:05:00.876 --> 01:05:05.046 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to overcome the most powerful obstacles,

01:05:05.046 --> 01:05:08.008 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and that same product of holy spirit

01:05:08.008 --> 01:05:10.218 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
will help us do the same.

01:05:10.218 --> 01:05:14.514 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, throughout the centuries,
just like today,

01:05:14.514 --> 01:05:16.933 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God’s servants, such as Daniel,

01:05:16.933 --> 01:05:20.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
have been made powerful,

01:05:20.020 --> 01:05:24.941 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
not by natural strength, but through faith.

01:05:24.941 --> 01:05:27.736 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So dear brothers and sisters,

01:05:27.736 --> 01:05:30.071 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
faithful children,

01:05:30.071 --> 01:05:32.616 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
cherished interested ones,

01:05:32.616 --> 01:05:35.118 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
pray earnestly for faith.

01:05:35.118 --> 01:05:38.497 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Put up a hard fight to maintain your faith.

01:05:38.497 --> 01:05:41.041 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And trust with all your heart

01:05:41.041 --> 01:05:43.043 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that if you have faith,

01:05:43.043 --> 01:05:46.379 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
maintain your faith, and walk by faith,

01:05:46.379 --> 01:05:49.049 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you definitely will see

01:05:49.049 --> 01:05:54.054 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
all of Jehovah’s promises fulfilled.

01:05:57.057 --> 01:05:59.184 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thank you, Brother Lett.

01:05:59.184 --> 01:06:02.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Your talk and this entire convention

01:06:02.729 --> 01:06:06.983 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
have strengthened our faith
and prepared us for future events.

01:06:09.277 --> 01:06:11.613 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
All in attendance will be pleased to know

01:06:11.613 --> 01:06:14.241 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that Parts I and II of the drama 

01:06:14.241 --> 01:06:16.827 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<i>Daniel: A Lifetime of Faith</i>

01:06:16.827 --> 01:06:20.413 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are available now for download on jw.org

01:06:20.413 --> 01:06:23.542 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and in the <i>JW Library®</i> app.

01:06:26.670 --> 01:06:30.590 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This convention is further proof that Jehovah

01:06:30.590 --> 01:06:33.301 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and his Son, Jesus Christ,

01:06:33.301 --> 01:06:36.471 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
provide abundantly for our spiritual needs

01:06:36.471 --> 01:06:39.558 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
