01:06:39.558 --> 01:06:43.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How we rejoice to be in their loving care!

01:06:43.395 --> 01:06:46.481 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And on behalf of the Governing Body

01:06:46.481 --> 01:06:49.943 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and all the hardworking members
of our Bethel families

01:06:49.943 --> 01:06:53.321 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and translation offices around the world,

01:06:53.321 --> 01:06:55.657 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we thank you for watching

01:06:55.657 --> 01:06:59.411 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the 2021 regional convention program.

01:06:59.411 --> 01:07:01.413 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We love you.

01:07:01.413 --> 01:07:04.875 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May your love and faith remain strong,

01:07:04.875 --> 01:07:08.044 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and may your hope remain bright.

01:07:08.044 --> 01:07:11.506 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
From the World Headquarters
of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

01:07:11.506 --> 01:07:14.134 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this is JW Broadcasting®.

01:07:16.094 --> 01:07:18.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s conclude now by singing a song

01:07:18.555 --> 01:07:22.350 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
