that faith has in our lives.

01:07:22.350 --> 01:07:25.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Please join in singing the original song

01:07:25.729 --> 01:07:27.981 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“With Eyes of Faith,”

01:07:27.981 --> 01:07:30.817 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
